body:
Have you ever wanted an improved version of Vanilla Minecraft that doesn't change the games default graphics all too much? Then you've come to the right place!

Welcome to FBVM ( A.K.A: Flip's Better Vanilla Minecraft ), A modpack that aims to improve Vanilla 1.19.2 Minecraft by adding certain Quality of Life features and Optimizations to make the game run better and 
it also features improvements in the game's graphis without changing the game's art-style drastically.

-------------------------

A few of the features this modpack includes are:

-Better Combat;

-The Fresh Animations Resource-Pack;

-Accurate Block Placement;

-Better F3;

-Continuity;

-And much more!

-------------------------

Hope you enjoy!
